					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"If anything, Misaki’s admission only added fuel to the fire. The younger Hanamaru sister’s brow is already furrowed in bewilderment.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
