				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"Being company commander means there’s a long check list of things to do before the big event. I wanted to make sure everything was perfect too, so we checked everything together.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"作为中队长，最后一天有许多事要确认──我也很期待明天的活动可以顺利，就跟郁子一起到处确认各地方的准备情形。",
